# =============================================================================
# Saved configs (user-specific)
# Pattern exclui exports timestamp-named do tool. Whitelist específico
# pros 2 presets que rastreamos como referência de hardware atual.
# =============================================================================
odrive_config_*.json
!Odrive-Wheel/tools/odrive_config_2026-05-06T16-33-53-630Z-Hoverboard.json
!Odrive-Wheel/tools/odrive_config_2026-05-07T21-49-59-444Z_Servo18Nm.json
odrive_config_dump.txt
odrive servoconfig.json
Odrive config.txt

